13 of Radon Professionals;
14 (b) One (1) nonvoting member shall be a representative of the home building
15 industry and shall be appointed by the Governor from a list of three (3) names
16 submitted to the Governor by the Home Builders Association of Kentucky;
17 (c) One (1) nonvoting member shall be a real estate salesperson or broker
18 licensed under KRS Chapter 324 and shall be appointed by the Governor from
