20 Association of Realtors;[ and]
21 (d) Two (2) members[One (1) member] shall represent[be a representative of] a
22 public health organization and shall be appointed by the Governor from a list
23 of four (4)[three (3)] names submitted to the Governor by the Kentucky
24 Cancer Consortium; and
